Flappy Buc Reqs

must have tap to interact feature
can have custom background
players win after passing through 100 pipes
player fails when the playable character touches a pipe (obstacle)
character will continuously fall in place with gravity 
tapping interaction allows character to fly upwards
        1 tap = 1 flap of wings upward
player failts if the character falls off the bottom of the screen
avatar doesn't move horizontally, only vertically by falling and flying
pipes slide thorugh the screen from the right side of the screen
pipes are attactched to the top and bottom of the screen
pipes exit through the left side of the screen, gives illusion of character flying forward when 'stil' obstacles are moving past them


